[SN]TITLE[SN]
Man and woman die in Aberdeen bike smash

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A man and a woman in their 20s have died in a crash involving a motorbike and a car in Aberdeen.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The fatal collision took place at 20:50 on Wednesday in the city's Hilton Drive.
The road was closed until about 02:00 to allow for accident investigation work.
Police Scotland said inquiries were continuing and asked for anyone who witnessed the crash, or had information about it, to contact them.
